        "nodes": [
            {
                "parameters": {
                    "content": "## Service Worker Template (Exec Trigger) E2E Tests\n\n**Before running:**\n1) Import `service-worker-template-generic-longtask-exec.json`\n2) Set `worker_workflow_id` in **Init Test Context** to that workflow's ID\n3) Ensure Postgres is running with `secure_task_scheduler.sql` installed\n4) Configure Postgres credentials for all DB nodes (Worker PostgreSQL)\n\n**What this tests:**\n- enqueue tasks\n- execute worker subworkflow 3 times\n- verify tasks are completed\n\n**Output:** Final node returns a summary with per-test results.",
                    "height": 300,
                    "width": 500,
                    "color": 2
                },
                "id": "38f6fed2-0a53-43f6-ab90-e3d70f9bb34b",
                "name": "Sticky Note",
                "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
                "typeVersion": 1,
                "position": [
                    528,
                    -128
                ]
            },
            {
                "parameters": {},
